			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>That is correct.  If you start the song and do not stop it at all, the charm never breaks.  I used to do that when I was lower level.  I'd charm one mob and start beating on another and have charmed mob assist me.
<br />

<br />
If you stop singing it, it wears off and you'd have to do as you would with any of our higher level charms.  Make new pet, out of old or a new one.  As with all charms, you cannot charm a charmed mob.  You have to wait for charm to wear off before you can recharm them.</span></td>
